<br>
We set up on the hill, and start pulling... everything's hunky-fucking-dory.  Gargs are decent AA exp at that level, the monk's doing a good job.  Attos appoints himself ML without a word said, but that's OK - I know clerics probably get shafted on dot costs, having them loot is probably a good way to make sure they can at least cover their costs.<br>
<br>
Attos loots a blue diamond, then announces a parchment drop.  Cool - I suggest that casters roll on all the parchments, and the melees can roll on the gem drops afterwards.  Attos says no, everyone should roll on parchments, and he should get all the gems to cover his peridot costs.  Last time I checked, one blue diamond buys about one point five metric assloads of peridots - I tell the group that everyone will roll on the big gems, and that if Attos keeps track of his expenses, we'll reimburse him afterwards from the cash split.  And I appoint the ranger as ML.<br>
<br>
I know - it's fucking plat.  I wasn't there for loot, I doubt anyone was, but when someone starts claiming BDs like that, I start to wonder about them.<br>
<br>
Another pull, all's well... I finish the fight at half health, and the monk goes to pull another.  I'm kinda expecting an elixir or something to top me up - I'm only 61, with mediocre gear, and those gargs hit pretty hard.  No heal.  Mob gets into camp, I grab aggro, it bends me over and introduces me to its interestingly textured stone fist... no heal.  The shaman starts spamming chloroblasts on me, I drop to 15%, no slow yet because the shaman is healing me... Attos finally stands up and casts... and fizzles.  A couple of seconds later, I die.<br>
<br>
From my cozy bind point in the Bazaar, I send a polite inquiry to the group: &quot;Attos, what the FUCK was that?&quot;  Attos disbanded.  Attos gated.  Attos left an unslowed mob in camp with only a ranger to tank it, and a shaman to heal.  The ranger died, the rest of the group made it out... and Attos didn't say a word.<br>
<br>
So, this is for Attos, you precious little fuckmitten, you...<br>
<br>
You suck.  More specifically, you suck hairy, sweat-drenched goat balls.  You spent the entire fucking group bitching and moaning, bragging about how close you were to your CoD key, whining when we got adds and you actually had to use some of your precious fucking mana, and looting every fucking thing in sight.<br>
<br>
If you like trying to induct tanks into your own little purple club, ask how many goddamned hp they have first.  If you don't want to cast any heal other than CHeal, have the fucking common sense to start your CHeal at more than 20% health - yes, asshat, even pimp Erudite clerics fizzle sometimes, accept it, deal with it, and fucking take it into account.<br>
<br>
And if seeing &quot;Attos, what the FUCK was that?&quot; on your screen after you sat on your ass and watched the tank die offends you so much... get the fuck out of Norrath, you little bitch, and go back to sucking your Daddy's cock for candy while he pats your head and calls you sweetums.<br>
<br>
This may have been an isolated incident.  Attos may be the nicest damned cleric in the world, a really swell guy who volunteers at the Humane Society and spends Sundays reading Bible stories to the children at the orphanage.  But tonight, to me, he was an asshat, a fuckmitten, and a petty little shit.  And I needed to get that off my chest.  Thanks for listening, and if this is all beneath you, and you don't care - why the fuck did you read it?<br>
<br>
-Thorokin <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=psykopathtz>Psykopath TZ</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(2/20/03 3:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1942.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Attos, you utter fuckmitten...</span><hr size=1> [quote]. Last time I checked, one blue diamond buys about one point five metric assloads of peridots[/quote]<br>
