<br>
   Consequently, it is traditional among many groups to let the cleric loot.  Sometimes, the cleric gets more than his fair share.  Usually, though, it balances out, because there are plenty of groups where the cleric loses money because the drops are almost non-existent.  WCY in PoN was that way, Dragon Gate in PoV is the same way, as is Flappies in PoStorm.<br>
<br>
    From your account, you... a) bitched at the cleric about loot,  b) bitched at the cleric about his healing, and then c) Wondered why he left.  Granted, he should have probably rezzed you.  I can't recall the last time I've left someone unrezzed, except maybe because of LD's.<br>
<br>
                                        something to think about...<br>
<br>
